reviewText: I PURCHASE LOTS OF MOVIES FROM AMAZON & I TRY TO GIVE THE LOW BUDGET FILM MAKERS A CHANCE, BUT PLEASE DO ALL THE CONSUMERS A FAVOR & LET US KNOW THAT THE MOVIE WE ARE ABOUT TO PURCHASE WAS FILMED WITH A HAND HELD CAMERA...ONCE AGAIN, THE QUALITY OF THE MOVIE WAS IN GOOD CONDITION.

This script could've been a " bigtime" suspense movie without all the stereotyping.. A beautiful women predator in a dating environment., And the men never expecting the "grim reeper"... The movie was watchable, It needed more suspense & finesse...
